[[Get List of GPG Keys]] then [[Get GPG Key Id]] by copying it.

``` bash
gpg --armor --export $KEY_ID > public.asc
```

store it somewhere safe! you'd also like to see how to [[Import GPG Public Key Into Your Keyring]] for further operations
